00:28:08.241 --> 00:28:09.201
about it to people.

00:28:11.401 --> 00:28:12.721
I am interested in it myself

00:28:12.721 --> 00:28:16.241
but I wouldn't be very good at it at all.

00:28:23.561 --> 00:28:26.601
