00:31:02.161 --> 00:31:04.401
I think there is a class society

00:31:04.401 --> 00:31:09.401
and I think public schools
may help its continuance.

00:31:11.441 --> 00:31:13.121
- At 35 in Sylhet

00:31:13.121 --> 00:31:14.921
he is teaching the older students.

00:31:15.841 --> 00:31:19.361
- I see education as
a key to it all I mean once

00:31:19.361 --> 00:31:23.161
your population becomes
educated it can think for itself

00:31:23.161 --> 00:31:25.881
a lot more and create wealth
and create opportunities.

00:31:25.881 --> 00:31:29.441
Good, because you've
